  "texts": [
    "Prompt quality and security analysisOverall, Impromptu is a useful tool for ensuring different quality aspects.",
    "Whereas \"quality\" in general is a broad term that might encompass several diverse metrics, we outline here examples of how our proposal can impact some specific dimensions to be considered in prompt engineering.",
    "As shown in Section 4.3, it is possible to generate validation artifacts, such as prompt-driven tests, to automatically assess whether the output of a generative AI tool for a given prompt fulfills the input specification.As demonstrated in Section 5, Impromptu already provided higher consistency and enhanced the maintainability of a prompt template library used in real-world applications.",
    "It mainly reduced the time and effort required for extending and managing the library and diminished the probability of manually-introduced errors.For prompts with parameters, an area of particular interest is checking whether the prompt is susceptible to prompt injection, i.e., crafting malicious inputs to achieve goals contrary to the interests of the prompt creators, such as revealing the content of the prompt in the output.",
    "Multi-lingual prompt generationGiven that the prompt generation process is under our control, we can generate the platform-specific prompts in languages other than English, provided that the user either (a) specifies literals in that language or (b) uses only predefined traits."
